#: ../../peps/peps/pep-0684.rst:646
msgid ""
"In addition to Py_NewInterpreter(), you can use "
"Py_NewInterpreterFromConfig() to create an interpreter. The config you pass "
"it indicates how you want that interpreter to behave."
